    <item>
      <title>Shivmaanaspooja - शिवमानसपूजा</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/shivmaanaspooja/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/shivmaanaspooja/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Shiva.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;शिवमानसपूजा 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9C&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9C&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Shivmaanaspooja 
    &lt;div id=&#34;shivmaanaspooja&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#shivmaanaspooja&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;audio controls&gt;
  &lt;source src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/006-ShivMaanasPooja.mp3&#34; type=&#34;audio/mp3&#34;&gt;
  Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio&gt;     
&lt;p&gt;रत्नैः कल्पितमासनं हिमजलैः स्नानं च दिव्याम्बरं &lt;br&gt;
नानारत्नविभूषितं मृगमदामोदाङ्कितं चन्दनम् । &lt;br&gt;
जातीचम्पकबिल्वपत्ररचितं पुष्पं च धूपं तथा &lt;br&gt;
दीपं देव दयानिधे पशुपते हृत्कल्पितं गृह्यताम् ॥१॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;सौवर्णे नवरत्नखण्डरचिते पात्रे घृतं पायसं &lt;br&gt;
भक्ष्यं पञ्चविधं पयोदधियुतं रम्भाफलं पानकम् । &lt;br&gt;
शाकानामयुतं जलं रुचिकरं कर्पूरखण्डोज्ज्वलं &lt;br&gt;
ताम्बूलं मनसा मया विरचितं भक्त्या प्रभो स्वीकुरु ॥२॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
